    • isOneOf

      public boolean isOneOf()
      Determines if it's sufficient for there to be at least one of the selectors present. If the value is false, then the scores are calculated proportionally to the number of selectors present. If the value is true, then the score is set to the maximum score for the category if at least one selector is present.
